Untitled

dd <- data.frame(
  date = seq(date_yq(2012, 4), date_yq(2018, 4)),
  V1 = 1:25
)

ggplot(
  dd,
  aes(
    x = date,
    y = V1
  )
) + 
  geom_point() +
  scale_x_date_yq()

ggplot(
  dd[get_year(dd$date) %in% 2014, ],
  aes(
    x = date,
    y = V1
  )
) + 
  geom_point() +
  scale_x_date_yq()

print each quarter

ggplot(

ggplot(
  dd[get_year(dd$date) %in% 2013:2014, ],
  aes(
    x = date,
    y = V1
  )
) + 
  geom_point() +
  scale_x_date_yq()
